# project setup

.initialize a project directory
[source,bash]
----
mkdir project
cd project
zig init
----

all source files live in src directory

# build binary executable

.build a binary executable file
[source,bash]
----
cd project
zig build
----

this runs build.zig
and creates an executable binary in zig-out/bin directory

# run binary
[source,bash]
----
./project/zig-out/bin/project

this runs the binary

# build run
[source,bash]
----
cd project
zig build run
---

build and run in one go
IMPORTANT: naming convention;	 project/src/main.zig

# build test
[source,bash]
----
cd project
zig test --summary all

with this flag even a succesful test gives feedback

